name: nytimes
text: A video of Joe Biden answering questions during a television interview has been edited to claim, incorrectly, that he was using a teleprompter. The modified clip has been shared by people close to President Trump, including his son Eric. https://t.co/n4sp48vrRp

name: nytimes
text: Asked by a reporter on Wednesday whether he would “commit here today for a peaceful transfer of all power after the election,” President Trump demurred. “We’re going to have to see what happens,” he said. https://t.co/lN1pyx4ulU
